                <head>No. 138.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Lowell</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Frelinghuysen</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">London</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1882-08-26">
                            <hi rend="italic">August</hi> 26, 1882</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>O’Mahoney was discharged 4th of August. Case of Brophy is being considered. Have
                    heard nothing from Secretary of Ireland concerning cases of Meany or George.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>LOWELL.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
